response.biography_en: I am an Italian entrepreneur with over 20 years of consolidated experience in the real estate investment sector on 4 continents. Believing immediately and personally in the opportunities that emerged from the dawn of a new era, today I have managed to build a network of 18 offices in 3 continents which has more than 3,000 partners around the world.
